1
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:18,200
<i>[Meet Yourself]</i>

2
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:23,400
<i>[Episode 14]</i>

3
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:32,400
Your village is ridiculous.

4
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:36,000
A groundless rumor has spread like its the truth.

5
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:40,000
The next rumor would be our child turning a year old.

6
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,700
That's how it is in the countryside.

7
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:44,000
Once they're done talking about you, they'll start on the next person.

8
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,600
Everyone thinks rumors are true.

9
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:50,300
In the end, these rumors are exaggerated beyond belief.

10
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,400
The kids even went to the courtyard to look at you.

11
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,600
It was a great chance to refute.

12
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:57,100
Why didn't you tell them the truth?

13
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:58,300
What can I say?

14
00:01:58,300 --> 00:02:01,800
They'll know who I am once I start clearing the air.

15
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:04,000
What's with your warped logic?

16
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,000
You were so eager to wallop A'Yuan and me

17
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:09,200
out of anger when we wronged you.

18
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:11,600
You're exaggerating.

19
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:15,200
Now that you have a chance to clear your name, you don't do a thing.

20
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,400
What's there for me to say?

21
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,600
I'll be leaving soon.

22
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,700
We're here!

23
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:29,000
- Over here!
- I dragged Damai over.

24
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,000
Have a seat.

25
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,400
Brother Guanjun, two colas.

26
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,600
- Okay.
- The food isn't ready yet.

27
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,800
What were you talking about.

28
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:37,800
We were discussing how I'll be left behind with this mess

29
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:40,100
after Xu Hongdou leaves.

30
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:41,000
You'll be fine.

31
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Just do what you need to.

32
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,200
Hongdou, are you leaving?

33
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,800
Not now.

34
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:48,000
Well, why did Chairman Xie say he'll be left behind?

35
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Don't you know about Xie Zhiyao and me?

36
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,800
What happened to you two?

37
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,400
Xu Hongdou.

38
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:58,400
You sound like you're spreading rumors about yourself.

39
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,000
What rumors?

40
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,600
The rumor in the village is that

41
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:08,000
Hongdou is Chairman Xie's ex-girlfriend from Beijing.

42
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:11,500
She has come looking for him, and they've reconciled.

43
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:14,400
That's not all. They'll be getting married soon.

44
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,400
Well, are you two getting married?

45
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,200
What do you think?

46
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:24,800
I think there's a chance.

47
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:29,800
Both of you fit the bill for marriage.

48
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,300
What bill?

49
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,900
Both of you are single.

50
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,900
I didn't realize it until you mentioned it.

51
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,400
That's a hard fact.

52
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,700
It's true!

53
00:03:39,700 --> 00:03:43,500
There's a romantic trope of marriage before love.

54
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:45,000
It's popular among readers.

55
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,000
The stories are very sweet.

56
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:51,000
Stop sighing.

57
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,500
Things will get better once I leave.

58
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:54,200
Persevere.

59
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,000
How can you leave?

60
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:59,000
Once you leave, there'll be new rumors

61
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,800
about Chairman Xie's girlfriend dumping him again

62
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:05,400
because she can't stand the countryside.

63
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,800
That makes sense.

64
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:10,000
Hey, Xu Hongdou. You're horrible!

65
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,600
How am I supposed to find a girlfriend in the future?

66
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:16,600
If a woman despises you because you've been dumped before,

67
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:19,000
then she doesn't deserve your love.

68
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,000
That makes sense.

69
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,000
Right?

70
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,400
Here you go.

71
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,600
This is extra spicy.

72
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,500
This one has regular spiciness.

73
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,500
These aren't spicy.

74
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,000
Thanks, boss.

75
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,100
If you marry A'Yao,

76
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:40,000
you'll be able to eat here for free.

77
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,800
That's such a great deal!

78
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:44,100
Why are you giving her free meals, when I don't get them?

79
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,800
What has that got to do with you?

80
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,900
Mind your own business.

81
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:55,000
- I won't go to the cafe tomorrow.
- Why not?

82
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,700
- I'm hanging out with others.
- With who?

83
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:58,000
These two.

84
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,500
Tomorrow is my day off, too.

85
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:03,600
Damai always stays in her room. No one can ever lure her out.

86
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:06,600
She's finally inviting us out.

87
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,700
We have to grant her wish.

88
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:13,200
Okay, have fun.

