♫ <i>Standing in the road</i> ♫

91
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:37,600
♫ <i>Don't know where to go</i> ♫

92
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:42,000
♫ <i>In the air, my memories flow</i> ♫

93
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,600
♫ <i>Faces in a row</i> ♫

94
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:48,400
♫ <i>Take a long way home</i> ♫

95
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:55,300
♫ <i>But all of this reminds me to believe</i> ♫

96
