00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:54,900
We just met and chatted a few times.

517
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:57,339
At most, we could be friends. Right?

518
00:27:57,339 --> 00:27:59,400
You know what he said to me?

519
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:04,400
He said I could move in with him when I felt like it.

520
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:06,300
Why should I live with him?

521
00:28:06,300 --> 00:28:10,200
He said he'd empty out half his closet for me.

522
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:15,600
We barely know each other, okay?

523
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:17,000
Yes.

524
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:19,300
You have to rain!

525
00:28:19,300 --> 00:28:22,200
I want it to rain for a whole year! You hear me?

526
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:23,800
Mr. Hu.

527
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:25,600
There's a plush toy in the back seat.

528
00:28:25,600 --> 00:28:27,300
Pass it to me.

529
00:28:27,300 --> 00:28:28,400
Okay.

530
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:32,000
There, there.

531
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:40,100
Why do have this in your car?

532
00:28:40,100 --> 00:28:42,200
Xiao Hu Lu left it here.

533
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,400
Quick.

534
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:47,000
My mom doesn't like girls like you who don't put on makeup.

535
00:28:49,900 --> 00:28:52,200
I burst out laughing.

536
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,600
Then, I bought a model kit.

537
00:28:53,600 --> 00:28:55,700
Guess how much it was.

538
00:28:55,700 --> 00:28:57,100
¥2,800.

539
00:28:57,800 --> 00:28:59,700
- That's expensive!
- Is it?

540
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:01,600
It's just a model kit worth ¥2,800.

541
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:03,300
Is that expensive?

542
00:29:04,300 --> 00:29:05,400
I bought it without much thought.

543
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,600
Is she crying?

544
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:08,500
Play Truth or Dare with her.

545
00:29:08,500 --> 00:29:10,500
- Why do we have to play that?
- You scared me.

546
00:29:10,500 --> 00:29:11,800
Hear this.

547
00:29:11,800 --> 00:29:13,800
That beast wanted to break up with me,

548
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:15,400
but he even asked me for milk tea money.

549
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:17,200
What are you talking about? I know it all!

550
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:21,000
He bought me milk tea with discount coupons.

551
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,000
Do you know? He didn't pay!

552
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,400
- What's going on?
- Of course not!

553
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:24,800
Then, he said

554
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:27,400
I won't ask you for the bus fare.

555
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:31,800
Then, my dad forced me to go on a jog.

556
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:34,500
After that, he persuaded me to find a job.

557
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:37,400
I have zero inspiration.

558
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:50,200
Damai is too tactiturn.

559
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:52,200
That's everything suppressed within her.

560
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:56,400
It's cold.

561
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:57,600
My mom says the same thing.

562
00:29:57,600 --> 00:30:01,600
That's why you should chat with us more often.

563
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:04,000
This feels amazing.

564
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:05,800
If you were not drunk,

565
00:30:05,800 --> 00:30:12,200
we'd never know about your relatives, your aunt, your date,

566
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,800
your ¥2,800 model kits,

567
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:16,600
and your dad forcing you to go jogging.

568
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:18,500
Incredible.

569
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:20,600
I'm going to quit drinking.

570
00:30:20,600 --> 00:30:22,400
Hongdou, you too.

571
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,900
Hongdou was even more ridiculous.

572
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:27,000
She kept crying

573
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:29,800
and listening to "Looking Back" again and again.

574
00:30:29,800 --> 00:30:31,800
Her tears wouldn't stop.

575
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:38,200
Oh, that rabbit plushie soaked in your tears belongs to Xiao Hu Lu.

576
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:41,400
Remember to wash it and return it to Chairman Xie.

577
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:46,600
I want to go home.

578
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:54,800
Here are the sausages.

579
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:02,000
- Where are you going?
- I want to take down the clothes.

580
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:04,499
Do that later. Eat first or the food will get cold.

581
00:31:04,499 --> 00:31:06,600
Don't mind it. I'll take these down.

582
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:08,000
I can do it after the meal.

583
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:09,700
Don't bother.

584
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:11,600
Why are there so many clothes?

585
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:13,800
- Mom.
- Sister, leave her be.

586
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:15,700
She won't heed a word you say.

587
00:31:15,700 --> 00:31:18,400
Don't criticize her. Do you even listen to me?

588
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:22,000
Didn't I tell you to stop contacting Luo Quan unnecessarily?

589
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:24,500
I didn't. He keeps sending messages to me on WeChat.

590
00:31:24,500 --> 00:31:26,600
He sent messages to me, too.

591
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:28,900
He's sending you messages because you reply to him.

592
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:30,800
If you stop replying, he'll stop too.

593
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:33,000
I didn't reply.

594
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:35,400
Well, did you like his posts on Moments?

595
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,600
He liked mine.

596
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:39,100
Can you block him?

597
00:31:39,100 --> 00:31:42,600
I have nothing to hide. Why should I block him?

598
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:48,000
You have to stop treating Luo Quan as our relative.

599
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:49,500
He'll get married eventually.

600
00:31:49,500 --> 00:31:51,400
If he's so chummy with his ex-wife's family,

601
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:53,700
what would his wife and her family think?

602
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:55,000
We have to keep up appearances.

603
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:57,000
You're putting in too much effort!

604
00:31:57,000 --> 00:32:00,400
Mom, are you angry?

605
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:04,200
No, I'm not.

606
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:06,900
Why are you so cranky?

607
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:11,800
I'm not cranky. I'm just talking louder.

608
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:13,700
Have your breakfast.

609
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:29,800
Luo Quan!

610
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:33,200
I told you to call me directly!

611
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:35,100
Don't you understand?

612
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:41,300
Mom.

613
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,000
I thought it was Luo Quan.

614
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:46,400
Why didn't you call me with your phone?

615
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:49,000
You're too lazy to get it?

616
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:51,800
Do you want to talk to Xiao Hu Lu?

617
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:52,800
Hu Lu, come over. Hu Lu!

618
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:55,200
It's your grandma. Hurry up.

619
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,600
Grandma, we're having breakfast.

620
00:32:58,600 --> 00:33:01,000
Do you miss me?

621
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,400
You don't have to miss me.

622
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:06,200
My mom said she'll send me over to you during the holidays.

623
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:08,400
I have a social engagement today.

624
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:10,000
She has a social engagement?

625
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:12,000
Today is the birthday of my good friend, Huzi.

626
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:15,200
So, I have to socialize this afternoon.

627
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:16,400
Honghong is going back to Guangzhou,

628
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:17,800
so she wants to hold the birthday party in advance.

629
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:20,100
Look at her. Shes busier than the village director.

630
00:33:20,100 --> 00:33:23,000
Okay, I'll pass the phone to grandma.

631
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,700
Me?

632
00:33:30,200 --> 00:33:32,100
Shuyu, we're good.

633
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:34,300
You're getting by well, too. Right?

634
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:40,200
Why didn't you use your phone?

635
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:42,000
I bet she's asking Mom to persuade Mr. Bow Legs to go on blind dates.

636
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:43,600
Interesting.

637
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:49,000
Sorry, sorry. I'm to blame.

638
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:55,600
Stop keeping in contact with him.

639
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:14,500
What's wrong, Sister Xiaochun?

640
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:16,000
What's up?

641
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:24,900
Your face is like a brooding yaksha in a temple.

642
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:31,500
My relatives are a mess.

643
00:34:31,500 --> 00:34:36,800
A distressing relative always calls us.

644
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:39,600
Even my mom has to persuade him to go on blind dates.

645
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:41,800
I'm annoyed to the bone.

646
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:45,400
That means you're on good terms.

647
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:47,400
This only happens between people who get along.

648
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,700
Who wants to be on good terms with him?

649
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:50,600
Get lost! Begone!

650
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:52,500
As far as possible!

651
00:34:58,600 --> 00:35:00,900
We still have one Peach Blossom to make.

652
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:05,900
This is the cafe where Na Na works at.

653
00:35:05,900 --> 00:35:07,200
It's very cosy.

654
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:09,000
So, I'm not cooped up indoors.

655
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,200
I leave my room.

656
00:35:10,200 --> 00:35:14,200
I even hung out with Hongdou and Na Na yesterday.

657
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:17,800
<i>How can you girls go to a bar? That's a rowdy place.</i>

658
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,600
It's not!

659
00:35:19,600 --> 00:35:23,400
Mr. Hu is a very talented singer at our courtyard.

660
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:25,500
That's a sober bar run by his friends.

661
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:29,000
It's a place to listen to music.

662
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:31,100
Na Na is here.

663
00:35:31,100 --> 00:35:32,400
Let me introduce them.

664
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,800
My parents.

665
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:36,600
Hello. Nice to meet you.

666
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,600
<i>Hello.</i>

667
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:38,600
<i>Hello, Nana.</i>

668
00:35:38,600 --> 00:35:42,500
<i>Thank you for celebrating Qingtian's birthday.</i>

669
00:35:42,500 --> 00:35:43,900
You're welcome.

670
00:35:43,900 --> 00:35:45,600
Damai always helps me out.

671
00:35:45,600 --> 00:35:47,800
She makes supper for me all the time.

672
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:49,400
<i>Oh, she knows how to take care of others?</i>

673
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:51,000
She's great at it.

674
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:53,800
<i>Na Na, does she go out?</i>

675
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:56,000
O-Of course, I do!

676
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:59,300
<i>Would a darned lass like you go out?</i>

677
00:35:59,300 --> 00:36:02,300
Yes, she does. I take her out to explore.

678
00:36:02,300 --> 00:36:04,300
All right. Let's end the call.

679
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:05,400
I need to write my draft.

680
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:07,400
I'll send videos. I'm hanging up.

681
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:10,500
<i>Move about after writing for an hour.</i>

682
00:36:10,500 --> 00:36:12,000
<i>Do eye exercises!</i>

683
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,500
I know. I do them.

684
00:36:13,500 --> 00:36:16,400
<i>Also, destiny brings people together.</i>

685
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:19,900
<i>Those who treat you well are your benefactors in life.</i>

686
00:36:19,900 --> 00:36:21,800
<i>They're precious gems.</i>

687
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:24,500
<i>Get along well. Don't quarrel.</i>

688
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:26,800
Roger that, Mr. Zhou.

689
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,600
Same here, Mr. Zhou.

690
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:29,900
<i>All right. Goodbye.</i>

691
00:36:29,900 --> 00:36:31,400
Okay, I'll hang up. Bye-bye.

692
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,600
The class is finally over.

693
00:36:34,600 --> 00:36:36,000
Let's eat.

694
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:38,800
Na Na.

695
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:41,400
- Let me have a look over there.
- Okay.

696
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:43,200
Na Na!

697
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:45,500
Yes?

698
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:53,300
Let me pick you up from work when I'm free.

699
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:59,100
Just like my parents said, I should leave my room more often.

700
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:02,400
Is this some kind of joke?

701
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:04,500
Will you ever have free time?

702
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:06,500
I will do my best to overcome this.

703
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:08,200
I'll make time.

704
00:37:08,200 --> 00:37:09,600
Really?

705
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:11,500
Yes!

706
00:37:15,700 --> 00:37:19,900
Do you know how the wind is formed?

707
00:37:19,900 --> 00:37:23,300
Hot air travels toward cold air,

708
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:25,400
and a cold place warms up.

709
00:37:25,400 --> 00:37:29,600
Once this cold place gets warm, it'll flow to other colder areas.

710
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:31,700
A new gust of wind is formed.

711
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,600
What are you saying?

712
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:39,700
What does this have to do with the flow of wind?

713
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:42,900
I'm saying that...

714
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:50,600
You're a breeze that flowed to me.

715
00:37:50,600 --> 00:37:54,000
So, I'm inclined to flow to you, too.

716
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:57,500
I'll treat you well, much better.

717
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:03,400
Well, since I flowed to you,

718
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:05,800
our temperatures are the same.

719
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:08,400
How can you flow to me?

720
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,800
Silly girl.

721
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:15,000
Regardless, thank you.

722
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:17,000
I'll treat you even better, too.

723
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:19,600
I'll get to work.

724
00:38:25,100 --> 00:38:26,800
Make this one.

725
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:31,200
<i>[I bawl my eyes out on Xiao Hu Lu's toy rabbit]</i>
Xu Hongdou!

726
00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:38,400
I'm coming!

727
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:41,300
Don't worry. There's no rush. Take your time.

728
00:39:42,300 --> 00:39:44,100
There's no rush? Take your time?

729
00:39:44,100 --> 00:39:45,800
But you're hollering at my window.

730
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:47,000
Unscrupulous.

731
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:48,700
An unscrupulous man.

732
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:53,600
<i>[Thatched House]</i>
Let's go.

733
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:54,700
Just woke up?

734
00:39:54,700 --> 00:39:56,700
No, I was washing clothes.

735
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:58,800
Sure. Did you eat?

736
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:01,100
I had breakfast with Na Na.

737
00:40:03,600 --> 00:40:05,300
Why are you laughing?

738
00:40:05,300 --> 00:40:06,800
I was born with smiling lips.

739
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,800
My jovial face is natural.

740
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,700
Consider carefully.

741
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:13,800
A jovial face is different from the village beau.

742
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:16,200
You can only have one character setting.

743
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:19,900
Pony Prince sounds very positive, all right?

744
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:23,100
Let's talk about the warehouse's personnel.

745
00:40:23,100 --> 00:40:24,600
We'll start with Aunty Feng.

746
00:40:24,600 --> 00:40:26,800
She's in charge of customer service.

747
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:30,800
She's righteous and frugal.

748
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:34,700
It's hard for her to change her personality.

749
00:40:34,700 --> 00:40:37,400
In that case, take her off customer service.

750
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:38,400
Let someone else do it,

751
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:41,200
and get her to dispatch the goods.

752
00:40:41,200 --> 00:40:43,400
Customer service has long working hours,

753
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:45,000
and messages have to be sent even after work,

754
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:48,900
but it has a higher pay than the other jobs.

755
00:40:48,900 --> 00:40:53,200
She was very diligent in learning how to type just for this job.

756
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:55,000
Eventually, she grasped the ins and outs of the role.

757
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:57,500
Most importantly, she's dedicated to her job.

758
00:40:57,500 --> 00:40:59,800
I'm not speaking ill of the other ladies,

759
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:03,500
but she's more capable than many of them combined.

760
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:06,600
I've never met a boss like you.

761
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:07,800
This is how it is in the village.

762
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:12,500
They always say they saw me running around naked as a kid.

763
00:41:12,500 --> 00:41:14,800
They'll dish out your embarrassing past,

764
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:17,400
and you don't have any authority before them.

765
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:18,800
All right.

766
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:22,400
I'll try to brainwash Aunty Feng.

767
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:24,800
You can do it, Manager Xu. I believe in you.

768
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,400
I'll try my best.

769
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:28,600
You sure are modest.

770
00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:30,000
Are you okay?

771
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,800
Manager Xu!

772
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:41,100
Come here and check this!

773
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:43,900
They're asking for a refund because it tastes bad.

774
00:41:43,900 --> 00:41:46,200
Is this refund allowed?

775
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:47,400
Take a look.

776
00:41:50,600 --> 00:41:53,400
- Refund half the price.
- Refund half the price?

777
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:56,400
The customer isn't satisfied, so we'll make them happy.

778
00:41:56,400 --> 00:42:00,400
We can't invite losses, Manager.

779
00:42:00,400 --> 00:42:05,000
Aunty Feng, business always has profits and losses.

780
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:08,400
